SENATE . . . . . . . . . . . . . . No. 949
By Mr. Oliveira, a petition (accompanied by bill, Senate, No. 949) of Jacob R. Oliveira, Vanna
Howard, Michael D. Brady, James K. Hawkins and other members of the General Court for
legislation to create a Green and Healthy Public College and University Building Planning
Commission that will make recommendations for public higher education buildings relative to
energy efficiency, spatial adequacy, life safety, accessibility, indoor environmental quality and
public health. Higher Education.
